All of the equipment is backed by IronPlanet’s IronClad Assurance ® guaranteed inspection reports, which assure buyers that they have an accurate representation of equipment condition. 
About IronPlanet 
IronPlanet is the leading online marketplace for used heavy equipment and an innovative participant in the multi-billion dollar heavy equipment auction market. Since 2000, IronPlanet has sold over $4 billion of used equipment online and has built a database of more than 1.4 million registered users worldwide. IronPlanet connects buyers and sellers of used equipment with its exclusive IronClad Assurance ® buyer protection program and family of sites including IronPlanet ® , GovPlanet ® , TruckPlanet ® , Cat Auction Services, Kruse Energy & Equipment Auctioneers SM , allEquip ® and Asset Appraisal Services SM . IronPlanet is backed by Accel Partners, Kleiner Perkins Caufield & Byers, Caterpillar and Volvo. For more information, visit www.ironplanet.com .
